Simple query script for stats.xonotic.org

Installation:
  * On Arch Linux, you may install from the AUR the 'xonstat' package;
    see https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/xonstat-git for details.
  * Otherwise, copy the xonstat script into a directory that is in your
    $PATH.

Usage:
  xonstat <player-id>

License:
  GNU GPL3
